    "An extensive application further highlights the relationship between a widely used accuracy metric and our model importance metric.",
    "The implication of this work is that our proposed importance metric provides novel insights, offering new information beyond traditional accuracy metrics.",
    "Our method provides a solid theoretical basis and clear criteria for quantifying a component model's contribution to ensemble performance.",
    "Moreover, leveraging the importance metric has the potential to incentivize original modeling approaches, thereby fostering a diverse landscape of perspectives among modelers, ultimately enriching the forecasting ecosystem.",
